OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FBreezier on Wednesday and slightly
OL,7,Fless hot, but remaining warm or very
OL,8,Fwarm to end the week. Often sunny but
OL,9,Fa small chance of showers or
OL,10,Fthunderstorms. Cloudier on Friday.
